subject Post-interview reminder for "#{application.name}"
html
  | Hi #{email},
  br
  | We hope your interview went well =) This is your post-interview reminder for "#{application.name}" to record any notes from the interview.
  br
  br
  - var applicationUrl = getExternalUrl(application.url);
  b
    a(href=applicationUrl) Click here to update your application notes
  br
  br
  b= "Posting URL: "
  a(href=application.posting_url)= application.posting_url
  br
  b= "Application link: "
  a(href=applicationUrl)= applicationUrl
  br
  b= "Interview link: "
  - var interviewUrl = getExternalUrl(interview.url);
  a(href=interviewUrl)= interviewUrl
  br
  br
  | We have schedule a follow-up reminder for you in 7 days. It will remind you to check in to prevent falling between the cracks.
  br
  br
  b
    = "Follow-up reminder ("
    a(href=applicationUrl) edit reminder
    = "): "
  //- Mon Mar 14 at 2:00PM CST
  = application.waiting_for_response_reminder.date_time_moment.format('ddd MMM D [at] h:mmA zz')
  br
  br
  | - The Find Work team
